name: The Deep-Sea Podcast - official logo
description:
The official logo of The Deep-Sea Podcast - a punk take on a science podcast about everything deep sea. The world's deepest podcast, having recorded an interview at 10km/6miles under the ocean:
https://youtu.be/7u-mIgKAzcQ

Top 5% of podcasts globally (verified by Listen Notes)
